07/10/2004
BUCHAREST, Romania -- The opposition National Liberal Party and Democratic Party alliance on Wednesday (6 October) formally nominated Bucharest Mayor Traian Basescu as its candidate for the November presidential election. 
He replaces former Prime Minister Theodor Stolojan, who pulled out of the race for health reasons at the weekend. 
(Nine o'clock, Rompres - 07/10/04; AFP - 06/10/04)
